{"word":"H3787 - כָּשֵׁר - kâshêr - kaw-share' - Direct","slug":"H3787","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">כָּשֵׁר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kâshêr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kaw-share'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Direct"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DB;&#x05BC;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E8; - ka&#x0302;she&#x0302;r</b> - <i>kaw-share'</i><p/>A primitive root properly to be <i>straight</i> or <i>right</i>; by implication to <i>be acceptable</i>; also to <i>succeed</i> or proser: - direct, be right, prosper."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3574\">H3574</a>, <a href=\"#/H3601\">H3601</a>, <a href=\"#/H3788\">H3788</a>"}]}